{"tid":640703,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"Superorganism - 2017出品音樂LSD","createTime":"2018-04-24T12:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T01:15:23.000Z","uid":33875,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e80f14988ec4b5054b812da7d0bf50afe82a8e","tid":640703,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c9tLaMV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc9tLaMV.png&h=ee65ea5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>Superorganism</strong></span>共有八位成員，主唱係剛剛18歲既日本妹Orono（右上2），鍵琴手Emily（左上2），結他手Harry（左下2），鼓手Tucan（左下1），整迷幻MV既Robert Strange（左上1），剩返兩位女仔Ruby、B，同韓仔Soul就係和音同伴舞。初時知道有韓日隊員，以為Soul係日本人，Orono係韓國人&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nEmily、Harry、Tucan為隊中創作主力，同Robert Strange之前係indie band <strong> The Eversons</strong>既成員。<br />\n<br />\nOrono本來係美國讀緊高中，睇睇下Utube聽到The Eversons，之後隊band去左日本表演，Orono睇完Show同佢地做左朋友。無幾耐發現Orono識唱歌，就搵佢錄左首Demo擺上網，就係後來既《Something For Your M.I.N.D.》，首歌一炮而紅，仲比Fifa 18擺左入OST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://consequenceofsound.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/superorganism.png?w=807\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fconsequenceofsound.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F03%2Fsuperorganism.png%3Fw%3D807&h=4cdd0d20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次聽係比Orono灰暗絕望既聲線吸引，然後愛上左玩味重、無套路但好完整既編曲，再睇埋KEXP Live Performance，Ruby、B、Soul既舞蹈配合，就感受到「Superorganism」中，由多個「個體」組合而成既強大感染力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>Superorganism - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AwLfWDb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAwLfWDb.png&h=3bdb453b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NM52w9xrdn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNM52w9xrdn4&d=eGD4uhieo%2FJ1%2Ft8wCdr7FjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=571db2e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NM52w9xrdn4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一樣引起話題既，就係佢地既MV，口味重，評價兩極化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMV主角有Hologram Orono，外星如來佛Soul，蝦，海豚&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SyzYYcC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSyzYYcC.png&h=cbe22065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kXdmkzg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkXdmkzg.png&h=51462468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人話佢地MV好似食左LSD見到既野，但佢地官方網頁有隻網頁遊戲，更加迷幻&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://escapetheinter.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fescapetheinter.net%2F&d=eGD4uhieo%2FJ1%2Ft8wCdr7FjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=370f8b26\" target=\"_blank\">http://escapetheinter.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5DupkAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5DupkAW.png&h=481d8079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSuperorganism特色唔單止係歌曲上，而係整體表演帶比觀眾既體驗，係水池邊拍打池水做伴奏，甚至咬蘋果、開汽水蓋，都係一場音樂表演中有作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想買碟可以係官方網站買，暫時有《SOMETHING FOR YOUR M.I.N.D.》 單曲黑膠，《SUPERORGANISM》同名專輯CD同黑膠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37db3698aeeca28f56b8ebc4214f2d5a7c79456","tid":640703,"uid":4610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"28ead46aea7f2c6024589e69fa2e34aa292d811b","tid":640703,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a37db3698aeeca28f56b8ebc4214f2d5a7c79456","tid":640703,"uid":4610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"Lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780b8bba2693deaf64c926b1b6c8cdfa1bc5f982","tid":640703,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59f2ae8e7588943d74bdf437056b292f1d155f6","tid":640703,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T10:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cb0a36642ef878b442633fd0e5399305a0dd31","tid":640703,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T10:55:16.000Z","msg":"Everybody wants to be famous<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到呢隊野都有人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始以為係meme嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2aae36166b05a7109c9af305bf829c0c2bb215","tid":640703,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3cb0a36642ef878b442633fd0e5399305a0dd31","tid":640703,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T10:55:16.000Z","msg":"Everybody wants to be famous<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到呢隊野都有人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始以為係meme嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif